name: Kickegg of the SpaceShipp
description:
Story
After a mission, the crew realised an alien boarded your ship and was eating it!

 After valiantly defeating it, the crew  saw... it layed eggs. Very bravely, they... ran away and asked you,  the cleaning robot,  to  help them.

Your mission, eject them.

By playing mini-golf.
